Frank Moran https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Moran 0 Francis Charles Moran (18 March 1887 – 14 December 1967) was an American boxer and film actor who fought twice for the Heavyweight Championship of the World, and appeared in over 135 movies in a 25-year film career.
